59:11.006 --> 59:12.223
(GASPS)

59:14.134 --> 59:15.386
(SHRIEKS)

59:20.182 --> 59:21.855
Oh, yeah!

59:22.059 --> 59:23.311
Ha-ha!

59:23.477 --> 59:24.820
