01:04:25.570 --> 01:04:26.913
(LAUGHS)

01:04:26.988 --> 01:04:29.832
Wrong end, sweetheart.

01:04:29.949 --> 01:04:31.075
(GASPS)

01:04:31.159 --> 01:04:32.285
(GROANS)

01:04:35.330 --> 01:04:36.331
(SHRIEKS)

01:04:36.414 --> 01:04:37.791
